Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.23,0:00:05.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將這片寂靜撕裂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.80,0:00:12.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引領整個世界\N來到熾熱之焰的最深處吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.29,0:00:26.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將我們的誓言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.06,0:00:35.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,灌注在朝天高舉的憤怒之拳中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.13,0:00:39.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再度點燃你的熱情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.30,0:00:42.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解放那沸騰不已的火紅熱血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.54,0:00:48.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論是誰都已無法阻止你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.98,0:00:55.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓一片黑暗的明天\N燃起希望的光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.39,0:01:00.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,化作捍衛弱者的獠牙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.92,0:01:03.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烈陽超重爆炎霸!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.36,0:01:15.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毫無畏懼的向前奔馳吧\N直到衝過那深紅色的終點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.41,0:01:24.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在最後一刻燃盡一切吧\N超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.12,0:01:36.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有的一切都已經...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.96,0:01:39.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,落入我的手中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.10,0:01:43.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再來就只剩下...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.60,0:01:46.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實捏碎而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.61,0:01:55.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.31,0:01:59.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在城內所有地方\N都沒有看到斗牙少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.85,0:02:05.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.26,0:02:13.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼先生?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.45,0:02:36.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,膽敢反抗我們的人類啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.22,0:02:38.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就好好去體會一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.29,0:02:41.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,體會自己有多愚蠢\N了解自己只是不完全的生命體吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.57,0:02:51.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修紀哥哥...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.91,0:03:00.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對於那些因痛苦而迷惘的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.14,0:03:03.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就賜予他們\N聚集時所能得到的領導與安全感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.38,0:03:05.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並且再給予其行動目的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.82,0:03:12.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「在重力衰弱的時刻」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.89,0:03:19.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你英司少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.96,0:03:22.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要找到斗牙少爺喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.53,0:03:24.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然放心交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.57,0:03:27.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定一定喔\N我們說好了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.60,0:03:30.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定一定!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.44,0:03:31.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我保證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.81,0:03:37.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保證...是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.45,0:03:39.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實英司...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.25,0:03:43.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.19,0:03:48.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我嗎?\N是我把他逼成這樣的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.56,0:03:50.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.36,0:03:54.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是金鋼飛拳\N還有必殺劍才對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.93,0:03:57.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好帥氣啊感覺好強啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.20,0:04:00.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可說是把男人的夢想與浪漫\N全都集結於一身呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.54,0:04:02.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這台超重神啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.47,0:04:03.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你懂不懂啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.77,0:04:05.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把諸多武器型兵器\N全部都裝備上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.08,0:04:10.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了會增加重量之外\N其他可是一點好處也沒有喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.65,0:04:11.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.68,0:04:16.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神與各武裝分開搭載的\N超重騎警比較起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.35,0:04:21.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機體的總合性能差太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.03,0:04:24.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知不知道你在放什麼屁!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.09,0:04:26.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不過就是EFA的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.60,0:04:29.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有駕駛一機\N搭載一種武裝的本事而已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.43,0:04:30.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.50,0:04:34.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這該不會是...點心吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.44,0:04:37.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯是"燒賣龍"的中華肉包喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.27,0:04:41.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太感謝妳了裘依露\N我肚子正餓呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.88,0:04:47.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們很了不起吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.35,0:04:48.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要再等個3天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.72,0:04:52.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重合神.神機超重神\N就能徹底復活啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.79,0:04:59.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜小姐的事...有沒有消息呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.14,0:05:12.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為被爆風炸飛的重鑽機\N艙蓋是完全打開的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.38,0:05:15.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很可能就這麼捲入爆炸之中了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.21,0:05:18.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事不可能的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.28,0:05:22.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為她可是琉菜小姐耶\N一定早就逃離了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.22,0:05:26.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.99,0:05:29.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我停止!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.06,0:05:36.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在幹什麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.33,0:05:39.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以哭喔...裘依露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.04,0:05:42.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經決定了\N在修好超重神之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.94,0:05:45.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是絕對不會哭的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.94,0:05:52.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果掉眼淚的話\N痛苦也會這麼流掉的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.69,0:06:02.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不想藉著哭泣\N來讓自己逃離這次悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.39,0:06:06.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我決定了我絕對不哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.10,0:06:11.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要背負著所有悲傷\N全力做好我現在能做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.57,0:06:14.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣一直奮戰下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.74,0:06:15.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.01,0:06:19.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信大家一定都沒事的是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.38,0:06:23.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.11,0:06:27.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在還不可以認輸對不對?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.72,0:06:29.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那還用說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.49,0:06:32.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了今晚也要來拼個通宵!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.79,0:06:37.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家會把你們\N整修的閃閃動人、又光又亮的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.89,0:06:41.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要問問題的是我才對吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.57,0:06:45.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.37,0:06:46.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.67,0:06:48.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重皇到底怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.74,0:06:50.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜的重鑽機呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.17,0:06:51.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.21,0:06:52.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家到底怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.41,0:06:55.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊...\N妳到底要我說幾遍才行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.85,0:06:59.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好歹也是傷患耶\N乖乖的回去床上躺著吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.88,0:07:02.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳們救了我我很感激
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.42,0:07:03.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但就算如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.05,0:07:07.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不表示EFA就有權力\N可以這樣拘禁我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.36,0:07:08.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.09,0:07:12.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等妳體內的G因子資料\N測量結束之後...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.53,0:07:15.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.13,0:07:19.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我失去意識的時候\N妳們有對我隨便亂來吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.27,0:07:21.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.94,0:07:23.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要做這種蠢事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.74,0:07:25.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是讓人看不下去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.34,0:07:30.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就連身為士兵最基本的\N自我控制都做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.18,0:07:35.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨便表達自己情緒的情形\N也太過頭了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.25,0:07:38.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,城琉菜...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.92,0:07:42.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我們徹底不同類型的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.26,0:07:46.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管什麼時候\N都只會想著同伴的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.56,0:07:49.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很直率的就把情緒表達出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.77,0:07:53.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還真是連一點戰士的自覺\N或尊嚴都沒有...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.27,0:07:55.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能把斗牙交給這種人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.21,0:08:04.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要駕駛超重神呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.95,0:08:06.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.18,0:08:08.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我就不可以呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.18,0:08:36.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了各位\N我會報答你們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.81,0:08:38.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.85,0:08:41.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准說這麼見外的話哦英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.75,0:08:46.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為斗牙已經是\N我們重要的朋友之一啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.39,0:08:47.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.59,0:08:50.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那雖然很趕但我們馬上...\N先等一下!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.99,0:08:52.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又來了怎麼現在還這樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.03,0:08:54.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快關機啦高須
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.56,0:08:55.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.93,0:08:59.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電視現在正在播出\N上次救了超重神的那些機體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.64,0:09:01.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼! 真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.57,0:09:06.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當超重神衝擊性的敗北時\N以壓倒性的戰鬥力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.64,0:09:11.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擊退外星異種的EFA新機動模組
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.35,0:09:15.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經從專家口中\N傳出證實存在的消息了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.95,0:09:20.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於量產型超重神.超重騎警\N政府將於本日正午
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.89,0:09:25.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於航行中的航空母艦\N多倫多號上進行的總統演說中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.00,0:09:28.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正式對外發表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.20,0:09:32.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於在我們眼前出現的超重騎警...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.60,0:09:36.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀白色的機體內\N到底隱藏著怎麼樣的性能呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.77,0:09:40.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不就是把超重神"亮"產\N然後去打倒外星異種嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.81,0:09:43.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下子就真的能安心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.48,0:09:45.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.96,0:10:01.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要快點回到戰線上哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.90,0:10:03.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們一起來...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.23,0:10:05.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保護地球的和平吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.17,0:10:09.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個訊號...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.41,0:10:11.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種是吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.31,0:10:14.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(本日關東地區天氣晴朗)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.64,0:10:17.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(但因位置不同)\N(有些地點會有雷雨出現...)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.58,0:10:22.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種現在正朝著北太平洋\N多倫多空母方向直行中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.93,0:10:34.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我聽好囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.20,0:10:37.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次作戰不但是你們的出道戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.77,0:10:43.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同時更是賭上我們人類未來\N以及一切未來的一戰喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.81,0:10:46.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊凡...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.05,0:10:53.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次作戰是不許失敗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.02,0:10:56.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盡全力去摧毀敵人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.49,0:10:59.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不說我也是這麼打算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.35,0:11:27.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是打從心底歡迎你的來訪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.05,0:11:29.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.89,0:11:39.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下降中的外星異種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.33,0:11:43.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將在186秒後\N與多倫多號航空母艦接觸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.17,0:11:45.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有找到斗牙嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.57,0:11:46.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼人呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.00,0:11:49.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才就一直通知...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.84,0:11:52.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻一點反應都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.78,0:12:01.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.68,0:12:03.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種急速接近中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.22,0:12:04.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經進入目視距離了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.75,0:12:05.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.89,0:12:07.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在還在甲板上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.26,0:12:08.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行快帶他去避難!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.89,0:12:09.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來不及了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.99,0:12:11.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種要與本艦衝撞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.86,0:12:12.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.70,0:12:16.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?發生了什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.70,0:12:19.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統所搭乘的空母被...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.50,0:12:21.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電波干擾情形太嚴重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.34,0:12:23.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空母的情形、外星異種的情形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.54,0:12:26.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都還無法進行確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.54,0:12:28.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等能夠確認的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.28,0:12:30.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再立刻通知我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.91,0:12:33.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷文先生?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.35,0:12:37.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統被...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.29,0:12:40.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經被打死了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.39,0:12:42.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不...還沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.70,0:12:55.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可思議的畫面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.74,0:12:58.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由超重騎警所發出的工學力場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.34,0:13:00.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經將外星異種困住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.54,0:13:03.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是新兵器的能力之一嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.81,0:13:05.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G戰將的各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.12,0:13:08.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全員出擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.25,0:13:09.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.22,0:13:11.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星辰群光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.42,0:13:12.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出動!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.63,0:13:25.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在就好好教教你\N誰才是這片天空中的女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.80,0:13:26.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在此刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.94,0:13:30.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們EFA引以為傲的\N地球新生守護天使們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.67,0:13:32.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"超重騎警"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.34,0:13:35.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始與外星異種作戰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.71,0:13:41.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們雖然在前次戰役中\N失去了偉大的英雄"超重神"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.38,0:13:42.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.72,0:13:44.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼之英雄的魂魄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.82,0:13:46.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在此時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.46,0:13:49.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又取得新的軀體而轉生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.06,0:13:52.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去! 隨便鬼扯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.29,0:13:54.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣\N那我就開超重皇去解決牠們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.83,0:13:56.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請看!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.33,0:14:00.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對鋼鐵惡魔處以天譴的\N鋼鐵天使們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.70,0:14:02.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看他們的英姿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.71,0:14:06.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重飛彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.62,0:14:15.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.75,0:14:18.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力放射標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.53,0:14:27.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由重力發電機所產生的\N重力子力場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.86,0:14:31.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當與裝甲或武裝構造結合的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.37,0:14:32.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重騎警...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.07,0:14:36.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會成為凌駕各式兵器的超兵器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.81,0:14:44.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德...曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.85,0:14:50.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好怕...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.99,0:14:54.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥他來殺我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.32,0:14:56.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.59,0:14:58.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你振作點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.16,0:15:03.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.70,0:15:08.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在展開工學力場的那一瞬間\N會出現空檔...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.64,0:15:12.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道超重皇這個弱點的\N只有我和...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.44,0:15:14.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修紀大哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.38,0:15:15.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到那個人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.91,0:15:17.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他居然還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.05,0:15:20.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都沒指望了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.52,0:15:24.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有指望了...一切都沒救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.82,0:15:26.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法為過去犯下的錯贖罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.99,0:15:29.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼躲進黑暗之中\N又對未來感到恐懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.09,0:15:32.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點出息也沒有的男人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.10,0:15:37.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誤把自己的美學當作真實的小丑...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.10,0:15:41.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是個愚蠢的男人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.70,0:15:43.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這個人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.88,0:15:51.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都走到現在了你還想要逃避嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.92,0:16:04.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了東西囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.53,0:16:07.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毀滅者之鑽!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.67,0:16:12.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.04,0:16:16.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕不是為了這副德性的你\N才繼承這張假面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.97,0:16:18.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.17,0:16:21.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是為了什麼\N才這樣一直努力奮戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.88,0:16:26.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了地球...\N為了讓妳們居住的這顆星球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.95,0:16:30.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要走上和我的星球相同的命運...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.62,0:16:32.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疾克!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.99,0:16:39.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了地球為了我們...\N雖然的確是這樣子沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.76,0:16:42.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是並不只是這樣吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.46,0:16:44.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這場戰爭是由你引起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.73,0:16:49.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該也要由你\N自己來親手做個了斷才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.84,0:16:52.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己的...戰爭...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.14,0:16:58.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就繼續縮在那邊發抖吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.35,0:17:02.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要踏上我所選擇的戰場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.58,0:17:04.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力強襲飛彈!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.53,0:17:12.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來交給我吧伊凡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.90,0:17:21.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開球囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.34,0:17:26.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重隕石射門!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.95,0:17:37.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們幾個居然都這麼威風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.72,0:17:40.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好! 那我就來負責最後的壓軸\N解決掉那個大頭目吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.86,0:17:51.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好猛啊!\N果然夠資格當我的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.00,0:17:54.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太適合當謝幕用的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.17,0:17:58.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我這一擊不就能拯救地球了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.37,0:17:59.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要來囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.51,0:18:03.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上送你一記必殺的超重光束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.15,0:18:09.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.32,0:18:11.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重光束居然毫無效果!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.66,0:18:19.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是我不對...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.70,0:18:27.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為不論面前\N到底有怎麼樣的命運在等著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.40,0:18:31.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都絕不該逃避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.51,0:18:36.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.18,0:18:39.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳綾香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.28,0:18:40.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.38,0:18:41.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.45,0:18:43.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回到我們的戰場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.35,0:18:48.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷文先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.46,0:18:49.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷文先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.96,0:18:52.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼先生呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.43,0:18:55.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓各位久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.70,0:19:01.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼先生!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.32,0:19:15.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼先生...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.78,0:19:19.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎讓各位掛心了\N還請各位見諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.26,0:19:22.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎您回來指揮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.13,0:19:25.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那...現在狀況如何了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.93,0:19:27.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時機已經到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.80,0:19:30.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此刻隨著這份光輝\N我們人類...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.33,0:19:31.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的地球!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.87,0:19:34.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都將自外星異種的魔爪中\N獲得解放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.27,0:19:39.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行! 那東西不可以破壞...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.11,0:19:41.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.85,0:19:48.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電光雷霆...轟炸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.76,0:20:01.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那道光...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.63,0:20:04.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥你終於想用那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.43,0:20:06.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來對付地球了是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.54,0:20:09.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太完美了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.84,0:20:12.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個"轟炸"是從哪蹦出來的呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.41,0:20:18.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,JACKOFF(回家吃自己吧)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.45,0:20:20.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敝人將與全人類一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.05,0:20:24.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將超重騎警的勝利\N視為我們的榮耀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.19,0:20:26.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭已經進入最後階段了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.82,0:20:29.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們將會把外星異種\N徹底的逐出地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.76,0:20:33.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敝人堅信超重騎警有能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.46,0:20:36.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以迅速達成此一任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.90,0:20:39.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個騙人的死老頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.17,0:20:43.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到底...做了什麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.04,0:20:48.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是人類...不\N這是所有地球人的勝利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.61,0:20:54.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重騎警將在正義之名下\N為人類帶來決定性的勝利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.38,0:20:58.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許現在就是需要的時候了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.99,0:21:02.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要能夠\N一掃這片陰霾的太陽光輝...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.23,0:21:04.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.26,0:21:08.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在是不是應該要\N迎接即將返航的鋼鐵天使們呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.30,0:21:10.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.70,0:21:12.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想見你們喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.83,0:21:15.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個人渣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.00,0:21:18.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別來弄髒我們這條街
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.07,0:21:21.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這死小鬼\N別只是給你好臉色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.08,0:21:23.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就開始得寸進尺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.68,0:21:27.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弄髒這條街的是你們才對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.66,0:21:34.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這丫頭...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.97,0:21:46.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的一點都沒變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.17,0:21:47.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全和以前的你一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.04,0:21:52.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.81,0:22:04.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因熱戀而無法成眠的夜晚\N已經看膩了星座占卜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.39,0:22:12.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為想要聽到人的聲音\N所以隨意打了電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.46,0:22:21.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了靠不住的語音留言\N你現在到底在哪裡呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.27,0:22:29.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,映著冰箱內的燈光\N我在狹小的宇宙裡彷徨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.28,0:22:37.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給我的唱片\N唱針已經跳開不知幾次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.55,0:22:44.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我相信這不變的溫度\N一直到什麼時候?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.09,0:22:46.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OHBABY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.73,0:22:52.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我耳邊輕語嘛\N對讓我聽聽你溫柔的聲音嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.50,0:22:55.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們手牽著手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.17,0:23:03.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一同被沁入你心中的\N淺淺呼吸籠罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.71,0:23:12.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我耳邊輕語嘛\N對讓我聽聽你溫柔的聲音嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.19,0:23:13.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們閉上雙眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.02,0:23:21.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一同在溜進你夢裡的\N甜美節奏中融化吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.07,0:23:28.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙到底怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.70,0:23:30.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有愛娜呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.21,0:23:31.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都還平安嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.61,0:23:34.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是不能把斗牙\N交給你們這種玩票性質的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.08,0:23:36.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼?\N這話是什麼意思!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.95,0:23:38.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我姓飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.15,0:23:40.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我比任何人都還要了解斗牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.62,0:23:43.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙就由我們超重騎警接收了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.59,0:23:45.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司快一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.42,0:23:47.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點幫幫斗牙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.22,0:23:49.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下回「紅之牙」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.46,0:23:52.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙你已經是我的人了


